==English==

===Noun===
'''[[illegal]] [[combatant]]'''
# a person who engages in combat without meeting the requirements for a [[lawful belligerent]] according to the [[laws of war]] as specified in the [[Third Geneva Convention]].

====Synonyms==== 
*[[unlawful combatant]]
*[[unprivileged combatant]]

